43
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,160
I'm next door.

44
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,640
Just call me anytime
if you need something.

45
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:32,760
Okay.

46
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,200
