I'm not afraid of her.

165
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:03,680
Keep your voice down.

166
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:06,400
Hide quietly in the washroom,
don't make any sound.

167
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,920
